  "findings": [
    "The Vera Rubin NVL72 rack unifies 72 NVIDIA Rubin GPUs and 36 NVIDIA Vera CPUs into a single integrated rack-scale system.",
    "Each GPU in the Vera Rubin NVL72 provides 3.6 TB/s of memory bandwidth, and the full NVL72 rack delivers 260 TB/s of aggregate bandwidth — described as more than the entire internet.",
    "The NVL72 scales with NVIDIA Quantum-X800 InfiniBand and Spectrum-X Ethernet networking to sustain high GPU cluster utilization while reducing time-to-train and total cost of ownership.",
    "The Vera CPU Rack is a dedicated rack-scale system containing 256 liquid-cooled Vera processors capable of sustaining more than 22,500 concurrent CPU environments, each running independently at full performance.",
    "The Rubin platform introduces a brand-new CPU, GPU, memory, and networking architecture across the entire stack."
  ],
